doctype html
html
  body
    div(style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0; padding: 30px 0;")
      table(width="80%", border="0", cellpadding="0", cellspacing="0")
        tr
          td(align="left", width="100%", style="font: 13px/18px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;")
            h2(style="font: normal 20px/23px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0 0 18px; color: black;")
              | Verify your changes!
            | Hello !{ user.full_name },
            br
            br
            | You are seeing this because you entered some credentials in the
            | !{ sitename }'s signup page and gave us an email. But because you
            | already have an account with the given email address us we just
            | wanted to verify that it was really you before we make any
            | changes.
            br
            br
            | Because you already have an account, your name and password are
            | the only things that will get updated.
            br
            br
            | You can safetly ignore this email if you did not request for this change.
            br
            br
            | Click <a href="!{ url }/api/auth/email/signup/modifyConfirm/!{ user.id }?token=!{ user.meta.signupVerifyToken }", style="color: #3366cc;">here</a>
            | to verify your changes. Or copy-paste this URL in your
            | browser. <a href="!{ url }/api/auth/email/signup/modifyConfirm/!{ user.id }?token=!{ user.meta.signupVerifyToken }", style="color: #3366cc;">!{ url }/api/auth/email/signup/modifyConfirm/!{ user.id }?token=!{ user.meta.signupVerifyToken }</a>
            br
            br
            | If you have any suggestions, questions or complaints send us an email at <a href="mailto:!{ webmasterAddress }", style="color: #3366cc;">!{ webmasterAddress }</a>
            br
            br
            | Best,
            br
            | The !{ sitename } Team
